<span id="freeTextContainer10510588779284614178">I always thought ornithology was kinda lame (sorry!). So I don’t know why I thought a book about describing someone’s bird watching outings would interest me (maybe because it was published by NYRB?).<br/><br/>Anyway, my rating is not based on how “good” I thought the book was, but rather how much I enjoyed it. The author is clearly a gifted writer and is passionate about his subject. I just don’t care much for the subject. </span>

